{"tid":2478588,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬民fb義賣　籌款撐平行政府","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:23:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1623df75ef9eaefad924f7b4d0ccc4f25e34a379","tid":2478588,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210407/2PLXB3OCWNB7ZL2TUIO7O7Z4HQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2F2PLXB3OCWNB7ZL2TUIO7O7Z4HQ%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtBY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=aa73d5d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2F2PLXB3OCWNB7ZL2TUIO7O7Z4HQ%2F&h=dbe19c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210407/2PLXB3OCWNB7ZL2TUIO7O7Z4HQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n緬民fb義賣 籌款撐平行政府<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8T-z86BE6Dox_6__Y014agKiy5A=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EBDNUZA6SRD2BLRS7HXLFXLMTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8T-z86BE6Dox_6__Y014agKiy5A%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEBDNUZA6SRD2BLRS7HXLFXLMTE.jpg&h=2a287a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■緬甸持續有民眾上街示威。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方暴力鎮壓下，親身參與示威活動屬高危。有民眾轉移陣地至網上，售賣物件或服務為平行政府委員會籌款。<br />\n<br />\n有示威者在社交媒體facebook群組出售物品，為緬甸聯邦議會代表委員會（CRPH）籌款，海外民眾亦可參與。有人在群組放售樂高積木（LEGO）的Marvel超級英雄系列，並在帖文上寫道：「雖然這不是很貴，但很難買得到。如果你展示CRPH捐款收據，可揀選任何一款。」亦有人放售K-Pop唱片及收藏品，同樣要求買家展示捐款收據，稱價高者得。<br />\n<br />\n除了放售實物，亦有人願意提供服務來籌款。有音樂家指可提供終身的結他及Ukulele課程；亦有戶外探險家稱可帶五人前往探險之旅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wbXL7Zde2uyhlj4Vl7tuKmVyOcc=/510x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2RQHQX5AFJAZXEX2ZZ4QCAAUEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwbXL7Zde2uyhlj4Vl7tuKmVyOcc%3D%2F510x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2RQHQX5AFJAZXEX2ZZ4QCAAUEQ.jpg&h=0c2b1dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有示威者發起「血印示威」。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噴紅漆悼烈士：血仍未乾<br />\n<br />\n政治犯援助協會（AAPP）指，政變至今有逾570名民眾喪生，包括47名兒童。該組織指，實際死亡數字料更高。有示威者在仰光道路上噴紅漆，悼念被士兵殺死的「烈士」，有人留言說：「血仍未乾。」亦有人將矛頭指向甘於遭上級操控的士兵：「別只為了低如狗糧售價的低微人工去殺人。」<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"763ef55c6b14bb600949f6f302223edb01ff7cdb","tid":2478588,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"唔反抗真係比人屠城<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}